name: Yassin MOHAMAD, Petitioner v. Ricardo C. JACKSON, Respondent

parties: Yassin MOHAMAD, Petitioner v. Ricardo C. JACKSON, Respondent.

opinions.text:
ORDER
PER CURIAM.
AND NOW, this 28th.day of February, 2013, the Application for Leave to File Original Process is GRANTED, and the Petition for Writ of Mandamus and the Application for Appointment of Counsel are DENIED. Finally, the Prothonotary is instructed to strike the name of the jurist from the caption.
opinions.author: PER CURIAM.

casebody.head_matter:
62 A.3d 374
Yassin MOHAMAD, Petitioner v. Ricardo C. JACKSON, Respondent.
No. 215 EM 2012.
Supreme Court of Pennsylvania.
Feb. 28, 2013.
